This is the goom sourcecode taken from CVS 
(http://sourceforge.net/projects/goom) and adapted for gmerlin.
Mostly costemic changes were done with the original code.

The original README follows below:

**************************
* What a GOOM! version 2 *
**************************
copyright 2000-2004, by Jean-Christophe Hoelt <jeko@ios-software.com>

This is my first visual plugins for XMMS, and I think that it's the best
I have ever done !

